Great, let's talk about what {MyHealth} has to offer you.

🟩⬜⬜⬜⬜

*Information from the experts*

24/7 access to health information right here on WhatsApp.

🟩🟩⬜⬜⬜

*Important reminders*

Health-related reminders, specific to you, when you need them.

🟩🟩🟩⬜⬜

*Help in a hurry*

Contact numbers and resources for emergencies.

🟩🟩🟩🟩⬜

*Someone to talk to*

Experts ready to help you with your health concerns.

🟩🟩🟩🟩🟩

*Progress tracking*

Whether it's your stress levels or pregnancy, I'll keep track of things.

I hope you've now got a good idea of what {service name} can do.

At this point, most people choose to create their profile. The more info you give me, the more control you have!

👇🏽 What do you want to do?
